				<wikidot:authorName>MemeFury</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4001485</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This gave me some real XCOM vibes with the psychic stuff from it. It also did a great job of making the soldiers still feel like people at the same time, however I did get confused at times with who was who; maybe giving more characterization to them will help in getting the reader to care about the characters, since it's obvious we're gonna see a sequel.</p> <p>Overall I loved it! A very good start imo. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
